
AI Insurance Agent

🚀 Overview

This project is an AI-powered Insurance Assistant that helps users get quick and clear answers about insurance topics. It is designed to respond only to insurance-related questions in a simple, accurate, and professional way.

🎯 Purpose

The AI Insurance Agent is built to:

Answer insurance questions clearly
Provide fast and simple explanations
Assist users with general insurance understanding
Avoid unnecessary or unrelated responses

⚙️ How It Works

User asks an insurance-related question
AI processes the query
AI returns a short and direct answer
If the question is not related to insurance, the AI will reject it politely

🧠 Features

Focused only on insurance topics
Simple and easy-to-understand responses
No coding or technical output
Strict filtering for non-insurance questions

🚫 Limitations

Does not generate code
Does not answer unrelated topics
Does not provide legal or financial advice

🎯 Example Use Cases

What is life insurance?
How does car insurance work?
What is covered under health insurance?
Understanding insurance terms
